# SQL Validation Checklist

## Pre-Migration Checks

- [ ] Backup existing data
- [ ] Note current table count
- [ ] Check for existing RLS policies

## Post-Migration Checks

### Tables (21 expected)
```sql
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM information_schema.tables 
WHERE table_schema = 'public';
```

### Seed Data
```sql
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM organizations;  -- 1
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM users;          -- 11
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tracks;         -- 7
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM playlists;      -- 3
```

### RLS Enabled
```sql
SELECT tablename, rowsecurity 
FROM pg_tables 
WHERE schemaname = 'public';
```

## Troubleshooting

If counts don't match, check Supabase logs for errors.
